# ifpdf

Convert PDFs into AI-friendly Markdown.

## Install

```bash
pip install ifpdf
```

## Usage

```bash
# Convert a PDF to Markdown
ifpdf paper.pdf

# Save to file
ifpdf paper.pdf -o paper.md

# Copy to clipboard
ifpdf paper.pdf --copy

# Process specific pages
ifpdf paper.pdf --pages 1-10

# Split into token-sized chunks
ifpdf paper.pdf --chunk-size 4000
```

